      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full configuration management, traceability, and independent verification of solver build required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Version control is in place and basic regression tests pass, but no independent third-party audit of the solver build has been conducted and configuration management records are incomplete. Achieved level falls substantially below required level for MRL 5."
    },
    {
