    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the breadth of activities conducted — including Monte Carlo UQ, multi-point experimental comparison, and systematic mesh refinement — collectively support a High assurance level. All thirteen credibility factors were assessed rather than scoped out, and the Monte Carlo analysis provides quantified uncertainty bounds on the primary hemolysis QoI. The team concluded that the model is acceptable for predicting absolute hemolysis levels for the VAD COU.",
